<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.9.3">
<l>tiruvuṭaip piḷḷaitāṉ tīya vāṟu</l>
<l rend="indent">tēkkamoṉ ṟumilaṉ tēcu ṭaiyaṉ</l>
<l>uruka vaitta kuṭattoṭu veṇṇey</l>
<l rend="indent">uṟiñci yuṭaittiṭṭup pōntu niṉṟāṉ</l>
<l>arukirun tārtam maiyani yāyam</l>
<l rend="indent">ceyvatu tāṉvaḻak kōya cōtāy</l>
<l>varukaveṉ ṟuṉmakaṉ taṉṉaik kūvāy</l>
<l rend="indent">vāḻavoṭ ṭāṉmatu cūta ṉaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no one to stop the wicked ways</l>
<l rend="indent">of this holy child, this radiant boy.</l>
<l>Having drunk [all] the butter in the pots</l>
<l rend="indent">that had been left to melt,</l>
<l>he continued going about throwing and breaking [them].</l>
<l>The wrong done to those in the neighbourhood,</l>
<l rend="indent">is this justice Yaśodā?</l>
<l>Call your son to come! O Madhusūdana! He won’t let us be!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
